Package: kickR
Type: Package
Title: Scrape FBREF team and player data
Version: 1.0.1
Author: Jeffrey Ohene
Maintainer: Jeffrey Ohene <jeffrey.ohene@aol.com>
Description: Scrape FBREF data for the Big 5 leagues (English Premier League,
    La Liga, Bundesliga, Serie A, and Ligue 1) as well as other leagues like
    the Belgian Pro League, Eredivise, Liga MX, MLS, Primera Liga, and the 
    Brazilian Serie A, etc. The package also equips you with the tools to 
    effortlessly save and export the scraped data to common formats for 
    further analysis. 
URL: https://github.com/jeffreyohene/kickR
BugReports: https://github.com/jeffreyohene/kickR/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    rvest,
    openxlsx
Suggests:
  testthat
Additional_repositories: inst
